<body>
<div><head>禮記新義疏</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-1a.2">鄭〈序〉：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-1a.3">「禮者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-1a.4">體也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-1a.5">其體有二。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-1a.6">一是物體，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-1a.7">言萬物貴賤高下小大文質各有其體。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-1a.8">二曰禮體，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-1a.9">言聖人制法，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-1a.10">體此萬物，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-1a.11">使高下貴賤各得其宜也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-1a.12">孔頴達《正義》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-2a.2">別同異，<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-2a.3">本同今異，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-2a.4">姑姊妹是也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-2a.5">本異今同，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-2a.6">世母叔母及子婦是也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-2a.7">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-2a.8">六十曰「耆」，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-2a.9">指使。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-3a.2">耆，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-3a.3">至也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-3a.4">至老之境也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-3a.5">六十耳順，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-3a.6">不得執事，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-3a.7">但指事使人也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-3a.8">《正義》。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-3a.9">陸德明《釋文》引上二句無「之」字。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-3a.10">君於大夫，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-3a.11">將葬，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-3a.12">弔於宮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-3a.13">及出，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-3a.14">命引之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-3a.15">三步則止。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-4a" ed="CHANT" n="001-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-4a.2">注：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-4a.3">出謂柩已在路。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-4a.4">路謂載柩之車。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-4a.5">《正義》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-4a.6">虞人致百祀之木，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-4a.7">可以為棺椁者斬之。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-4a.8">君者德著幽顯，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-4a.9">若存，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-4a.10">則人神均其慶，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-4a.11">沒，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-4a.12">則靈祗等其哀傷也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-4a.13">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-5a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-5a" ed="CHANT" n="001-5a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-5a.2">乃薦鞠衣于先帝。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-5a.3">在明堂。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-5a.4">《正義》引王權、賀場、熊氏等。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-5a.5">律中黃鐘之宮。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-5a.6">黃鐘是十一月管，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-5a.7">何緣復應此月？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-5a.8">正以土義居中，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-5a.9">故虛設律於其月，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-5a.10">實不用候氣也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-5a.11">十二律互相為宮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-5a.12">據律主言之也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-5a.13">《正義》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-6a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-6a" ed="CHANT" n="001-6a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-6a.2">蜡也者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-6a.3">索也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-6a.4">歲十二月，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-6a.5">合聚萬物而索饗之也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-6a.6">謂造此蜡祭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-6a.7">配此八神而祭。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-6a.8">《正義》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-7a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-7a" ed="CHANT" n="001-7a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-7a.2">冠而字之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-7a.3">敬其名也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-7a.4">注：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-7a.5">重以未成人之時呼之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-7a.6">重，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-7a.7">難也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-7a.8">難未成人之時呼其名，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-7a.9">故以字代之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-7a.10">《正義》引賀氏。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-8a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-8a" ed="CHANT" n="001-8a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-8a.2">雉、兔、鶉、鷃。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-8a.3">注：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-8a.4">又以「鷃」為「鴽」也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-8a.5">鴽，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-8a.6">蝙蝠。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-8a.7">《正義》云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-8a.8">皇氏用賀氏之說。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-9a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-9a" ed="CHANT" n="001-9a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-9a.2">芝栭、蔆、椇、<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-9a.3">栭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-9a.4">軟棗，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-9a.5">芝，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-9a.6">木椹也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-9a.7">《正義》引賀氏。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-9a.8">三牲用藙，<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-10a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-10a" ed="CHANT" n="001-10a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-10a.2">注：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-10a.3">藙，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-10a.4">煎茱萸也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-10a.5">《漢律》：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-10a.6">會稽獻焉。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-10a.7">《爾雅》謂之樧。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-10a.8">今蜀郡作之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-10a.9">九月九日取茱萸，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-10a.10">折其枝，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-10a.11">連其實，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-10a.12">廣長四五寸，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-10a.13">一升實，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-10a.14">可和十升膏，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-10a.15">名之藙也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-10a.16">同上引賀氏。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-11a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-11a" ed="CHANT" n="001-11a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-11a.2">魴、鱮烝，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-11a.3">雛<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-11a.4">《釋文》賀讀「魴鱮烝雛」為句。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-11a.5">左結佩，<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-11a.6">注：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-11a.7">結者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-11a.8">結其綬使不鳴。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-11a.9">事佩綬且不鳴，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-11a.10">今云「結綬使不鳴」，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-11a.11">則猶在佩玉也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-11a.12">《正義》引賀氏。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-12a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-12a" ed="CHANT" n="001-12a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-12a.2">廟中，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-12a.3">齊齊，<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-12a.4">齊，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-12a.5">在啟反。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-12a.6">《釋文》引賀音。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-12a.7">立容德，<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-13a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-13a" ed="CHANT" n="001-13a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-13a.2">德，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-13a.3">有所施與之名也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-13a.4">立時身形小俯嚮前，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-13a.5">如授物與人時也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-13a.6">故注云「如有予也」。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-13a.7">會前兩注也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-13a.8">《正義》引賀云。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-13a.9">俎用梡嶡，<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-14a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-14a" ed="CHANT" n="001-14a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-14a.2">直有腳曰梡，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-14a.3">加腳、中央橫木曰嶡。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-14a.4">《正義》引賀云。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-14a.5">男子冠而婦人笄，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-14a.6">男子免而婦人髽。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-14a.7">其義：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-14a.8">為男子則免，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-14a.9">為婦人則髽。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-15a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-15a" ed="CHANT" n="001-15a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-15a.2">男去冠，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-15a.3">猶婦人去笄，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-15a.4">義盡於此，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-15a.5">無復別義，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-15a.6">故云其義也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-15a.7">《正義》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-15a.8">期而祭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-15a.9">禮也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-15a.10">期而除喪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-15a.11">道也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-15a.12">祭不為除喪也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-16a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-16a" ed="CHANT" n="001-16a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-16a.2">祭為存親，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-16a.3">幽隱難知。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-16a.4">除喪事顯，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-16a.5">其理易識。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-16a.6">恐人疑祭之為除喪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-16a.7">故記者特明之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-16a.8">云「祭不為除喪也」。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-16a.9">《正義》引庾氏、賀氏。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-16a.10">夫為人後者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-16a.11">其妻為舅姑大功。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-17a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-17a" ed="CHANT" n="001-17a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-17a.2">此謂子出時已昏，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-17a.3">故比婦還，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-17a.4">則服本舅姑大功。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-17a.5">若子出時未昏，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-17a.6">至所為後家方昏者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-17a.7">不服本舅姑，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-17a.8">以婦本是路人，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-17a.9">來又恩義不相接，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-17a.10">猶臣從君而服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-17a.11">不從而稅，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-17a.12">人生不相及之徒，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-17a.13">而皆不責非時之恩也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-17a.14">《正義》引賀云。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-18a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-18a" ed="CHANT" n="001-18a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-18a.2">宗子，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-18a.3">母在為妻禪。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-18a.4">父在，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-18a.5">適子為妻不杖。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-18a.6">不杖則不禫。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-18a.7">若父沒母存，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-18a.8">則為妻得杖又得禫。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-18a.9">凡適子皆然。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-18a.10">嫌畏宗子尊厭其妻，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-18a.11">故特云「宗子，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-18a.12">母在為妻禫」。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-18a.13">宗子尚然，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-18a.14">則其餘適子母在為妻禫可知。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-18a.15">《正義》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-19a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-19a" ed="CHANT" n="001-19a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-19a.2">為慈母後者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-19a.3">為庶母可也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-19a.4">為祖庶母可也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-19a.5">雖有子道，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-19a.6">服於慈庶母三年，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-19a.7">而猶為己母不異，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-19a.8">異於後大宗而降本也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-20a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-20a" ed="CHANT" n="001-20a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-20a.2">下殤小功，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-20a.3">帶澡麻不絕本詘，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-20a.4">而反以報之。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-20a.5">下殤小功，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-20a.6">男子絰牡麻而帶澡，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-20a.7">婦人帶牡麻而絰澡。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-20a.8">故小功殤章云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-20a.9">「牡麻絰。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-20a.10">若依其次，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-20a.11">不應前帶，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-20a.12">故知前言男子之帶，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-20a.13">後言婦人之絰也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-20a.14">並同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-21a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-21a" ed="CHANT" n="001-21a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-21a.2">凡羞有湆者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-21a.3">不以齊。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-21a.4">凡湆皆謂大羹，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-21a.5">大羹不和也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-21a.6">《正義》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-21a.7">飲酒者、禨者、醮者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-21a.8">有折俎不坐。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-22a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-22a" ed="CHANT" n="001-22a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-22a.2">折俎則殽饌尊。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-22a.3">故〈冠禮〉：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-22a.4">庶子冠于房戶之前，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-22a.5">而冠者受醮不敢坐，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-22a.6">及禨者竝不敢坐也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-22a.7">案〈鄉飲酒〉、〈燕禮〉有折俎者皆不坐，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-22a.8">獨云禨者、醮者不坐者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-22a.9">以禨者、醮者無酒俎之時則得坐，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-22a.10">嫌畏有折俎亦坐，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-22a.11">故特明之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-22a.12">云「有折俎不坐」。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-22a.13">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-23a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-23a" ed="CHANT" n="001-23a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-23a.2">強而弗抑則易，<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-23a.3">師但勸強其神識，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-23a.4">而不抑之令曉，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-23a.5">則受者和易，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-23a.6">和易亦易成也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-23a.7">《正義》引賀氏。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-23a.8">禮、樂、刑、政，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-23a.9">其極一也，<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-24a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-24a" ed="CHANT" n="001-24a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-24a.2">雖有禮、樂、刑、政之殊，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-24a.3">及其撿情歸正，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-24a.4">同至理極，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-24a.5">其道一也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-24a.6">《正義》引賀氏。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-24a.7">欣喜歡愛，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-24a.8">樂之官也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-25a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-25a" ed="CHANT" n="001-25a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-25a.2">注：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-25a.3">官，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-25a.4">猶事也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-25a.5">八音克諧，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-25a.6">使物歡欣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-25a.7">此樂之事迹也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-25a.8">在心則倫類無害，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-25a.9">故為樂情。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-25a.10">在貌則欣喜歡愛，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-25a.11">故為樂事也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-25a.12">《正義》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-26a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-26a" ed="CHANT" n="001-26a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-26a.2">禮者別宜，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-26a.3">居鬼而從地。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-26a.4">以為居鬼者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-26a.5">居其所為，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-26a.6">謂若五祀之神，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-26a.7">各主其所造而受祭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-26a.8">不得越其分，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-26a.9">是不變化也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-26a.10">五祀之神造門，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-26a.11">故祭於門；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-26a.12">造竈，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-26a.13">故祭於竈，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-26a.14">故云「居」。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-26a.15">《正義》引賀氏。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-27a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-27a" ed="CHANT" n="001-27a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-27a.2">小大相成，<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-27a.3">十二月律，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-27a.4">互為宮羽而相成也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-27a.5">《正義》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-27a.6">終始相生，<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-28a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-28a" ed="CHANT" n="001-28a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-28a.2">五行宮商，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-28a.3">迭相用為終始。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-28a.4">同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-28a.5">「夫〈武〉之備戒之已久，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-28a.6">則既聞命矣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-28a.7">敢聞遲之遲而又久，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-28a.8">何也？」<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-29a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-29a" ed="CHANT" n="001-29a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-29a.2">備戒已久是遲，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-29a.3">久立於綴亦是遲。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-29a.4">而又久，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-29a.5">何意如此？<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-29a.6">《正義》引賀氏。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-29a.7">有三年之練冠，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-29a.8">則以大功之麻易之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-29a.9">唯杖、履不易。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-30a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-30a" ed="CHANT" n="001-30a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-30a.2">三等大功，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-30a.3">皆得易三年練衰。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-30a.4">其三等大功，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-30a.5">衰雖七升、八升、九升之布，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-30a.6">有細於三年之練衰，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-30a.7">以其新喪之重，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-30a.8">故皆易之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-30a.9">《正義》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-30a.10">女君死，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-30a.11">則妾為女君之黨服。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-30a.12">攝女君，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-30a.13">則不為先女君之黨服。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-31a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-31a" ed="CHANT" n="001-31a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-31a.2">雖是徒從而抑妾，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-31a.3">故為女君黨服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-31a.4">防覬覦也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-31a.5">攝女君，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-31a.6">則不為先女君之黨服者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-31a.7">以攝女君差尊，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-31a.8">故不為先女君之黨服。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-31a.9">皮弁一，<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-32a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-32a" ed="CHANT" n="001-32a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-32a.2">以素為衣裳也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-32a.3">玄端一，<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-32a.4">燕居之服，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-32a.5">玄端朱裳也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-32a.6">纁裳一，<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-33a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-33a" ed="CHANT" n="001-33a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-33a.2">冕服之裳也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-33a.3">亦可鷩、毳，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-33a.4">任取中間一服也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-33a.5">如有服而將往哭之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-33a.6">則服其服而往。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-33a.7">若新死者服輕，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-33a.8">則不為之制服。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-33a.9">雖不為重，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-33a.10">變而為之制服。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-33a.11">往奔喪哭之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-33a.12">則蹔服所制之服。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-33a.13">往彼哭之事畢，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-33a.14">反服故服也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-33a.15">並同上。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-34a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-34a" ed="CHANT" n="001-34a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-34a.2">己雖小功，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-34a.3">既卒哭，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-34a.4">可以冠，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-34a.5">取妻，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-34a.6">不殤之小功則不可。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-34a.7">小功下殤，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-34a.8">本是期親，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-34a.9">以其重，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-34a.10">故不得冠、取。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-34a.11">推此而言之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-34a.12">降在大功，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-34a.13">理不得冠、嫁矣。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-34a.14">《正義》引賀氏。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-35a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-35a" ed="CHANT" n="001-35a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-35a.2">女雖未許嫁，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-35a.3">年二十而笄，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-35a.4">禮之；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-35a.5">婦人執其禮。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-35a.6">十五許嫁而笄者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-35a.7">則主婦及女賓為笄禮。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-35a.8">主婦為之著笄，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-35a.9">女賓以醴禮之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-35a.10">未許嫁而笄者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-35a.11">則婦人禮之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-35a.12">無主婦、女賓，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-35a.13">不備儀也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-35a.14">《正義》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-36a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-36a" ed="CHANT" n="001-36a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-36a.2">皆升自東榮，<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-36a.3">注：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-36a.4">榮，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-36a.5">屋翼。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-36a.6">以其體下於屋，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-36a.7">故謂上下在屋，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-36a.8">兩頭似翼。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-36a.9">故名屋翼也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-36a.10">《正義》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-37a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-37a" ed="CHANT" n="001-37a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-37a.2">弔者襲裘，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-37a.3">加武帶絰，<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-37a.4">武，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-37a.5">謂吉冠之卷。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-37a.6">主人既素冠素弁，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-37a.7">故弔者加素升於武。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-37a.8">《正義》引賀氏。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-38a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-38a" ed="CHANT" n="001-38a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-38a.2">挋用浴衣，<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-38a.3">以布作之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-38a.4">生時有作也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-38a.5">〈士喪禮〉云「浴衣於篋」，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-38a.6">注云「浴衣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-38a.7">已浴所衣之衣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-38a.8">以布為之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-38a.9">其制如今通裁」是也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-38a.10">《正義》引賀氏。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-39a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-39a" ed="CHANT" n="001-39a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-39a.2">妻於夫拘之。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-39a.3">拘其衣食領之交也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-39a.4">夫於妻、於昆弟執之。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-39a.5">夫於妻執其心上衣也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-39a.6">於兄弟亦執心上衣。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-40a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-40a" ed="CHANT" n="001-40a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-40a.2">諸父、兄弟之喪，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-40a.3">既卒哭而歸。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-40a.4">此弟謂適弟，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-40a.5">則庶兄為之次，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-40a.6">云至卒哭乃歸也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-40a.7">下云兄不次於弟，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-40a.8">謂庶弟也。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-41a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-41a" ed="CHANT" n="001-41a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-41a.2">大夫畫帷，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-41a.3">二池，<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-41a.4">前後各一。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-41a.5">《正義》引賀氏。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-41a.6">天命之謂性，<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a" ed="CHANT" n="001-42a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.2">性之與情，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.3">猶波之與水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.4">靜時是水，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.5">動則是波；<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.6">靜時是性，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.7">動則是情。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.8">《左傳》云天有六氣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.9">降而生五行。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.10">至於舍生之類，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.11">皆感五行生矣。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.12">唯人獨稟秀氣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.13">故〈禮運〉云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.14">人者五行之秀氣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.15">被色而生。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.16">既有五常仁、義、禮、智、性，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.17">因五常而有六情，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.18">則性之與情，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.19">似金與鐶印，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.20">鐶印之用非金，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.21">亦因金而有鐶印。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.22">情之所用非性，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.23">亦因性而有情，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.24">則性者靜，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.25">情者動。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.26">故〈樂記〉云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.27">「人生而靜，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.28">天之性也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.29">感於物而動，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.30">性之欲也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.31">故《詩‧序》云「情動於中」是也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.32">但感五行，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.33">在人為五常，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.34">得其清氣備者則為聖人，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.35">得其濁氣簡者則為愚人。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.36">降聖以下，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.37">愚人以上，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.38">所稟或多或少，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.39">不可言一，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.40">故分為九等。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.41">孔子曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.42">「唯上知與下愚不移。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.43">二者之外，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.44">逐物移矣，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.45">故《論語》云：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.46">「性相近也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.47">習相遠也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.48">亦據中人七等也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2e1107_CHANT_001-42a.49">《正義》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
